  "title": "Operations / Engineering Support Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>We are a marine engineering service company looking for a reliable and detail-oriented person to support our daily operations and field engineers.</p><p>This role focuses on coordination, scheduling, and preparation, ensuring that engineers can focus on their work on-site.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Check vessel schedules and inform engineers of upcoming jobs</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with coordinators and vendors to arrange transportation</p></li><li><p>Prepare and check required spare parts for each job</p></li><li><p>Handle basic administrative tasks such as emails, simple documentation, and invoice support</p></li><li><p>Provide general operational support related to field activities</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Comfortable with scheduling, coordination, and communication</p></li><li><p>Basic proficiency in email and Excel</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented and responsible</p></li><li><p>Experience in marine or engineering-related industries is a plus (not mandatory)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Work Arrangement</strong></p><ul><li><p>Full-time</p></li></ul><p><strong>This role is suitable for someone who</strong></p><ul><li><p>Is good at organizing and coordinating tasks</p></li><li><p>Enjoys supporting field operations behind the scenes</p></li><li><p>Is adaptable and able to handle practical, day-to-day tasks</p></li></ul>",
